title: Only 1 session cookie for logged in users.

tosdr.case: This service does not track you
tosdr.tldr:
Resource https://tbs-mbs.net/
does NOT track user activity,
does NOT contain trackers.
How do I check it out?
Activate any ad-blocker and visit (refresh any page on https://tbs-mbs.net/ ).
The blocker will show the result.
